Tumble - Series 1, Episode 4




Show Four

The remaining (8) celebrities will perform whichever discipline they did not perform in Show 3 and once again receive comments and scores from the judges. Again these scores form the judges' leaderboard which will determine which celebrities are the 'bottom two'. These two will face 'the Vault'. One celebrity will be eliminated after the vault performance.




Original Air Date: 30-Aug-2014
